00:50:09,347 --> 00:50:11,547
Together!

856
00:50:09,347 --> 00:50:11,547
Together!

857
00:50:11,547 --> 00:50:14,547
And I didn't think that I would be here

858
00:50:14,547 --> 00:50:16,347
five years from the start with you guys.

859
00:50:16,347 --> 00:50:17,147
Same.

860
00:50:17,147 --> 00:50:17,547
Yeah.

861
00:50:17,547 --> 00:50:19,647
I really thought I'd be out of here.

862
00:50:19,647 --> 00:50:20,347
Same!

863
00:50:20,347 --> 00:50:21,447
Same.

864
00:50:21,447 --> 00:50:23,947
But now, I can't - I can't see a future

865
00:50:23,947 --> 00:50:26,047
where I'm not here with you guys, so...

866
00:50:26,047 --> 00:50:28,347
Aww! That's so sweet!

867
00:50:28,347 --> 00:50:30,047
Oh shush... okay...

868
00:50:30,047 --> 00:50:32,647
So because of that, I'm not gonna give up yet.

869
00:50:32,647 --> 00:50:34,247
I don't want to give up yet.

870
00:50:34,247 --> 00:50:35,547
So let's do our best!

871
00:50:35,547 --> 00:50:36,747
Doing our best!

872
00:50:36,747 --> 00:50:38,447
Oh yeah, the wrap-up jingle is playing!

873
00:50:38,447 --> 00:50:40,647
I'm just gonna start talking about nothing

874
00:50:40,647 --> 00:50:43,247
because it annoys me when they play the jingle to tell me to stop.

875
00:50:43,247 --> 00:50:44,447
Tell us! Tell us!

876
00:50:44,447 --> 00:50:46,247
This morning I ate a bagel

877
00:50:46,247 --> 00:50:47,547
and it had cream cheese on it. It was delicious!

878
00:50:47,547 --> 00:50:49,247
But it went over my macros,

879
00:50:49,247 --> 00:50:51,347
so I'm in big trouble with my trainer!

880
00:50:51,347 --> 00:50:52,647
It's fine, it's fine!

881
00:50:52,647 --> 00:50:54,747
Anyway, you can't get rid of me!

882
00:50:54,747 --> 00:50:55,947
Hahaha!

883
00:50:55,947 --> 00:50:58,447
You can't get rid of any of us, hopefully!

884
00:50:58,447 --> 00:51:01,547
Alright everybody, all good things come to an end, unfortunately.

885
00:51:01,547 --> 00:51:04,847
But thank you so much to the hololive EN community

886
00:51:04,847 --> 00:51:07,347
for supporting us continuously for five years.

887
00:51:07,347 --> 00:51:09,347
Thank you to the girls today

888
00:51:09,347 --> 00:51:11,447
and all the staff-san that supported us also

889
00:51:11,447 --> 00:51:13,847
for this celebration, who gave us the trophies!

890
00:51:13,847 --> 00:51:14,547
Yeah!

891
00:51:14,547 --> 00:51:17,047
Once again, congratulations to us!

892
00:51:17,047 --> 00:51:18,647
To us! Yay!

893
00:51:18,647 --> 00:51:21,247
To us! Oh yeah!

894
00:51:21,247 --> 00:51:23,247
Yeah! Thank you! Thanks everybody!

895
00:51:23,247 --> 00:51:25,347
Bye bye! Bye bye!

896
00:51:25,347 --> 00:51:26,947
Bye bye! Bye bye!

897
00:51:26,947 --> 00:51:28,247
Peace!

898
00:51:28,247 --> 00:51:30,047
Thanks! Go check out the merch!

899
00:51:30,047 --> 00:51:31,047
Check out the merch!

900
00:51:31,047 --> 00:51:32,147
Merch!

901
00:51:32,147 --> 00:51:33,647
Merch please!

902
00:51:33,647 --> 00:51:36,347
Ta-da! The merch announcement!

903
00:51:41,047 --> 00:51:43,247
次は、グッズのお知らせです！
Next is the merchandise announcement!

904
00:51:43,247 --> 00:51:47,547
ホロライブEnglish -Myth- 5周年記念グッズが発売されます！
We have hololive English -Myth- 5th Anniversary Celebration merch being released!

905
00:51:47,547 --> 00:51:50,347
詳細を見ていきましょう。チェックしてね！
Let's look at the details. Check it out!

906
00:51:50,347 --> 00:51:52,747
まずは、ミラーアクリルパネルです。
First up, we've got the Mirror Acrylic Panel.

907
00:51:52,747 --> 00:51:56,747
イラストの周囲や背景が金属質の鏡のような雰囲気になっています。
It's designed so that the surroundings and background of the illustration have a metallic mirrored vibe.

908
00:51:56,747 --> 00:51:59,247
うわぁ、すごくかっこいい！このイラスト、本当に大好きです。
Uh, so cool! I absolutely love this illustration.

909
00:51:59,247 --> 00:52:00,847
皆さんも気に入ってくれると嬉しいです。
Hope you guys do too.

910
00:52:00,847 --> 00:52:03,647
次は、コレクションカードです。
Next up, we have the collection cards.

911
00:52:03,647 --> 00:52:07,547
これらのカードは光沢のあるメタリック仕上げで、3種類のデザインから選べます。
These cards feature a shiny metallic finish, and you can choose from three different designs.

912
00:52:07,547 --> 00:52:10,947
また、裏面は全員でお揃いのデザインになっています。
Also, the backside is matching for us all.

913
00:52:10,947 --> 00:52:14,547
推しのカードをぜひ手に入れてくださいね！
Make sure to get the one from your oshi for sure!

914
00:52:14,547 --> 00:52:17,047
次は、コインメダルです。
Next up, we have the coin medals.

915
00:52:17,047 --> 00:52:20,347
ピカピカの5周年記念コインメダル！
Our shiny 5th anniversary commemorative coin medals!

916
00:52:20,347 --> 00:52:23,947
メンバーごとに1つのデザインがあり、裏面は共通のデザインになっています。
There's one design for each member, and the back side also has a common design.

917
00:52:23,947 --> 00:52:28,547
オリジナルのパッケージに入った、アンティーク調の金メッキ仕上げです。
They come in an antique gold-plated finish inside the original packaging.

918
00:52:28,547 --> 00:52:31,047
わぁ、すごくキラキラしてる！
Ooh, so shiny!

919
00:52:31,047 --> 00:52:35,547
わぁ、どれも良さそうですね！でも、次に紹介するものに特に注目しています。
Oh man, everything looks so good! But I'm especially interested in what we have to show you guys next.

920
00:52:35,547 --> 00:52:37,947
次は、アニバーサリーハットです！
Next up, we have the anniversary hats!

921
00:52:37,947 --> 00:52:41,447
まずは、アニバーサリーハット - 森カリオペ。
So first up, Anniversary Hat - Mori Calliope.

922
00:52:41,447 --> 00:52:43,547
柔らかくてふわふわした生地を使っています。
This one uses a soft, fluffy fabric.

923
00:52:43,547 --> 00:52:47,547
デス先生の部分は取り外し可能なので、なしで被ることもできます。
The Death Sensei part is removable, so you can also rock it without him.

924
00:52:47,547 --> 00:52:50,647
ぜひチェックしてください、すごくスタイリッシュです！この形が大好きなんです。
Make sure that you check it out, it's super stylish! I love the shape so much.

925
00:52:50,647 --> 00:52:54,847
メンバーのDead Beatsのみんなと一緒に投票で決めたので、皆さんに楽しんでもらいたいです！
And all of my member Dead Beats voted on it together, so hope that you guys will enjoy!

926
00:52:54,847 --> 00:52:57,847
次は私の！小鳥遊キアラのアニバーサリーハットです。
Next up, we have mine! The anniversary hat from Takanashi Kiara.

927
00:52:57,847 --> 00:53:00,847
こんな感じです！装飾パーツは取り外し可能です。
Looks like this! Decorative parts are removable.

928
00:53:00,847 --> 00:53:04,447
リバーシブル仕様で、裏返すと違う色になります！
It can be worn reversibly, inside out, so you'll have a different color then!

929
00:53:04,447 --> 00:53:08,747
今まで私にはなかったバケットハットのデザインです。すごくおしゃれですよ！
And it's a bucket hat style design, which we didn't have before for me. Very fashionable, I must say!

930
00:53:08,747 --> 00:53:12,347
最後は私の帽子！アニバーサリーハット - 一伊那尓栖。
Last but not least, we have my hat! The Anniversary Hat - Ninomae Ina'nis.

931
00:53:12,347 --> 00:53:16,047
リボンの部分は取り外し可能で、パッチもすごく可愛いです。
The ribbon part is removable, and the patches are super cute too.

932
00:53:16,047 --> 00:53:19,047
被ればタコダチになれます！イエス！
You can wear it to become Takodachi! Yes!

933
00:53:19,047 --> 00:53:23,147
リボンの有無で、色々なスタイルが楽しめます。
And yeah, you can mix and match with or without the ribbon for different looks.

934
00:53:23,147 --> 00:53:26,447
皆さん、ぜひグッズをチェックしてください！
So everybody, be sure to check our merch out!

935
00:53:26,447 --> 00:53:31,047
これで5周年記念配信を終了します！
And that concludes our 5th year anniversary stream!

936
00:53:31,047 --> 00:53:32,647
アルティメット・ミス！
Ultimate Myth!

937
00:54:09,247 --> 00:54:49,247
Thank you for an unforgettable 5 years! I can't wait for even more amazing things in the future! Buckle in! It's going to be an exciting ride ahead!! GO NEXT!

938
00:54:09,247 --> 00:54:49,247
Thanks for 5 years together, everyone! Are you ready for more?! It's already been the best journey a Reaper could ask for, but let's run forward into the future! I can't wait to see what the future holds for us and my Myth girls! Love you all! Goodbye for now!

939
00:54:09,247 --> 00:54:49,247
Thank you all for being here! These 5 years were super crazy with so many ups & downs but looking back, the good and happy memories are so much more! Every moment shared together will forever stay deep in my heart and I'm looking forward for more! Love you all so much! KIKKERIKI!!!

